{"tid":1551412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港好多傻閪仲成條懞撚咁，唔知有幾危險","createTime":"2019-09-08T03:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T10:21:53.000Z","uid":40250,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6f86791a380088042495cd1c7ce128fd8954532d","tid":1551412,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:57:28.000Z","msg":"見到呢班人都唔知好嬲定好笑<br />\n警狗同港共已經無視法治任何拘捕市民，然後折磨甚至毀屍滅跡，無視憲法限制隨意進入私人物業剝奪私有財產，最重要係做到咁盡都無香港人反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，中國以後會驚你？<br />\n<br />\n公權力會不斷擴張，而且速度非常快。到呢一刻有資產有能力移民個班人都仲當無事發生過，連美金同離岸戶口都未整，真係服撚左佢地。<br />\n<br />\n中美trade deal傾唔成，美國打新冷戰一定唔會留香港呢個窗口俾中國集資，一獲熟<br />\n<br />\n中美傾得成trade deal, 即係香港都無利用價值，呢三個月搞到咁撚大獲，中國會放過香港？ 即時沒收財產打你入集中營，歐美都當睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係我悲觀得制，定係佢地樂觀得制？"},{"pid":"ff2ad2da898d9f029244ffa7abae57dd3047b0bd","tid":1551412,"uid":268383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSeYxuJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSeYxuJ.jpg&h=40379b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6RPD9K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6RPD9K.jpg&h=82932c32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56772d8247dbda9c541004e66a274e21c2457eff","tid":1551412,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"仲有成班傻仔日日都講，著黑衫犯法阿？帶gear犯法阿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班弱智豬岩岩放監"},{"pid":"53a34516de25c245d118529b33754613d9e0f1d7","tid":1551412,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56772d8247dbda9c541004e66a274e21c2457eff","tid":1551412,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2